title: (PSX-PSP) Dracula 2:The Last Sanctuary converted properly (Kingd
description:
DRACULA 2 - THE LAST SANCTUARY:

The sequel to the Dracula: Resurrection game brings an even scarier adventure. It's 1904, Count Dracula has gone to ground in London. Find the secret of how to vanquish the Prince of Darkness and his Black Guard before they destroy you. Dracula 2: The Last Sanctuary revives some of the original characters and the novelist's spirit, to create a convincing sequel. Solve riddles through exploring and decision-making.


Tested and working on all CFW's 5.00 m33 and above using the 500 popsloader pack set on 3.72 POPS...KloWn
